{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Twisted Screens!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/AtariGif.gif?t=1738362972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Twisted Screens</i> invites you to step into the shoes of Tessa, a mercenary hired by ATR Industries to explore an abandoned science facility overrun by horrific experiments. Partnering with the snarky A.I. assistant, Legsy, Tessa embarks on a journey to uncover the dark secrets behind this once-renowned company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this first-person sci-fi thriller, explore the haunting ATR facility, solve intricate puzzles, and piece together the absurd lore of this bizarre world. Utilize gadgets and hazards to navigate challenges and fend off lurking enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/extras/Legsygif.gif?t=1738362972\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet Legsy, your witty companion! This sarcastic A.I., created during ATR\u2019s heyday, will guide you through the facility, assisting with puzzles and providing humorous commentary. Communicating primarily through a walkie-talkie, Legsy may even make a personal appearance when the situation calls for it.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738362972","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/page.bg.jpg?t=1738362972","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/df8a631d436eac28f379d46086065295cdd7c156/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738362972","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008950/df8a631d436eac28f379d46086065295cdd7c156/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=17383